---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Meetings">
  <p class="text-sm text-ink-subtle"><a href="/managers">← Managers</a></p>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-6">Meetings</h1>

  <p class="text-ink-muted max-w-2xl">
    The Advisory Group meets every two months. Meetings are open to
    ISO/TC 46 member-body liaisons; minutes are published here once
    ratified.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">Cadence</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
    <li>Months: February, April, June, August, October, December</li>
    <li>Format: virtual, 90 minutes</li>
    <li>Agenda closes 14 days before each meeting</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-ink-subtle">
    TODO: minutes archive populates from a meetings directory once
    added to the register repo.
  </p>
</Layout>
